text: Marcel Wildhaber (born 17 May 1985) is a Swiss cyclo-cross cyclist. ==Major results== ===Cyclo-cross=== ;2009-2010 : 1st Cyclocross Aigle ;2010-2011 : 1st Internationales Radquer Steinmaur, Steinmaur ;2011-2012 : 1st Internationales Radquer Steinmaur, Steinmaur : 1st Internationales Radquer Hittnau, Hittnau ;2012-2013 : 1st Flückiger Cross, Madiswil ;2013-2014 : 1st GP-5-Sterne- Region, Beromünster : 2nd National Cyclo-cross Championships ;2014-2015 : 1st Schlosscross, Rheinfelden : 1st National Trophy Series Round 4, Milton Keynes ;2015-2016 : 1st EKZ CrossTour Round 4, Eschenbach ;2016-2017 : 1st Overall EKZ CrossTour ::1st Eschenbach : 1st QianSen Trophy Cyclocross Round 2 , Changxindian Fengtai (Beijing) : 1st Internationales Radquer Steinmaur, Steinmaur ;2017-2018 : 1st Overall EKZ CrossTour ::1st Bern ::1st Aigle ===Mountain=== ;2013 : 1st 20px National Cross-country Eliminator Championships ;2015 : 1st 20px National Cross-country Eliminator Championships : 3rd European Cross-country Eliminator Championships ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male cyclists
title: Marcel Wildhaber
